title: Recommended plugins
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Installing following plugins will make the work with your [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com/]] easier:

* [[Relink|https://flibbles.github.io/tw5-relink/]] - When renaming a tiddler, Relink can update the fields, filters, and widgets of all other tiddlers.
* [[Edit-CompText|https://snowgoon88.github.io/TW5-extendedit/]] - This plugin adds completion when editing the body of a tiddler.
* [[TiddlyRemember|https://sobjornstad.github.io/TiddlyRemember/]] - A tool that integrates the TiddlyWiki with the spaced-repetition-flashcards tool [[Anki|https://apps.ankiweb.net/]]
* [[Streams|https://saqimtiaz.github.io/sq-tw/streams.html]] - Streams is a keyboard friendly way to write and easily divide your text into separate tiddlers while writing.
* [[Refnotes|https://kookma.github.io/Refnotes/]] - Refnotes is a set of macros and stylesheets for creating abbreviations, footnotes and citations.

See also recommendation for [[Bi-directional links]] plugins.